<span class="displaytext">santa fe, nm -- today, new mexico governor (candidate full) released the following statement on the tragic death of nine south carolina firefighters: <p>"firefighters are trained to make the ultimate sacrifice -- to walk into the worst danger and to risk their lives without hesitation. last night, nine south carolina firefighters ran into a burning building to protect the lives of their fellow citizens trapped inside. these firefighters taught us the true meaning of the words courage, honor, and duty." </p><p>"let us forever remember these nine brave firefighters, who gave their lives for others. let us, citizens of a grateful nation, allow our thoughts and prayers to rest today on these courageous citizens, these american heroes."</p></span>



